Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,餵 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,退下 連我迪奧·溫伯格都不認識了麽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,菲奧娜 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,果然那台Valiancer是迪奧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:21:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麽 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你該做的可不是在這種地方浪蕩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,父親？
